  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The overall goal of the study is to evaluate the safety, efficacy and therapy settings of the
      Hypoglossal Nerve Stimulation (HGNS) System for stimulating the hypoglossal nerve to help
      maintain airway opening in subjects with Obstructive Sleep Apnea (OSA).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
